      "id": "s1",
      "section": "Opening",
      "layout": "title",
      "tag": "Academic library",
      "title": "Library Modernization Roadmap",
      "subtitle": "Easton University Library Academic library",
      "notes": "Open by naming the decision: Shift the library from stacks-first to research-services-first."
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "section": "Context",
      "layout": "text-1x",
      "title": "Why This Matters",
      "text": [
        "Easton University Library should focus the next cycle on ",
        {
          "text": "shift the library from stacks-first to research-services-first",
          "bold": true,
          "color": "#F59E0B"
        },
        " while making the operating tradeoffs clear to academic library stakeholders."
      ]
    },
    {
